## Quick Start

```bash
# Install
cd sdk/python && pip install -e .

# Run storage contract probe
python -m concord.contract_probe /tmp/concord

# Run multi-agent demo
cd sdk/examples/multiagent
./start_agents.sh
python3 demo_feature_flag.py

# Run transport benchmarks
cd sdk/examples
python benchmark_transport_file.py --events 10000
```

